  <brief_title>The Paediatric Virtual Autopsy Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-mortem Cross-sectional Imaging With Guided Biopsy; A Comparative Study With Conventional Autopsy in Foetuses, Neonates, Infants and Children</official_title>
  <sponsors>
