  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Stillborn infants ≥ 16 0/7 weeks of gestational age (GA)

          -  Live born infants ≥ 16 0/7 weeks GA until adolescents up to 16 years of age, who died
             of natural- and non-natural cause (trauma, homicide, suicide and intoxication).

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Deceased infants who are donors of organs

          -  Lack of parental consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
